title: American Horror Story Cult Episode 2 Review
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This was a much better episode than the premiere !!
I think all of these crazy people around Ally are part of the cult and tbh they are hilariously messed up
Can you do a review for every episode this season
The neighbours were the ones who reported Kai getting beat up. They are definitely a part of the cult in my opinion.

Don't think for one minute Kai is not going to come back and throw her accidentally shooting Pedro, in Ally's face! It is gonna happen! It was so refreshing listening to her neighbors be that truthful. We think words hurt, but that's all perspective.
